name: Blue Belitong #2
description:
Belitung (or in English, Billiton) is an island on the east coast of Sumatra, Indonesia in the Java Sea. Recently, Belitung becomes famous because of Laskar Pelangi (The Rainbow Troops), a box office movie was directed by Andrea Hirata. 
I explored Belitung years ago and found out the beauty of the sea in there. I shot this photo  to describe the blue feeling.
